ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This is a required course for first-year anthropology graduate students concentrating in socio-cultural anthropology. The course outlines contemporary historical trends and developments in the discipline.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Readings and discussions in this course definitely helped to mold my dissertation and research interests. The historical contexts helped me better understand current trends in theoretical and methodological thought and practice.
